# Plan a collision-free joint path to a target end-effector pose and execute it.
# Target is either a saved pose (by name) or an inline pose (use_pose=true).
# The response returns once PLANNING completes; motion then runs asynchronously
# (watch /servo_node/status and /servo_node/plan_state). Nudging the sticks or
# pausing the servo aborts an in-progress motion.
string name                  # saved-pose name (ignored when use_pose is true)
bool use_pose                # true => target the inline `pose` instead of `name`
geometry_msgs/Pose pose      # target EE pose (base_frame) when use_pose is true
---
bool success                 # true => a path was planned and motion started
string message
